OL,3,CMan arrested following disorder after
OL,4,CMiddlesbrough match against Millwall
OL,6,FA man's been arrested on suspicion of
OL,7,Fviolent disorder following the
OL,8,FMiddlesbrough football match against
OL,9,FMillwall.
OL,11,FOfficers received reports of disorder
OL,12,Faround Middlesbrough railway station
OL,13,Fafter the game against their promotion
OL,14,Frivals on Friday 3 April, with
OL,15,Fopposing supporter believed to have
OL,16,Fbeen fighting.
OL,18,FCleveland Police are not aware of
OL,19,Fanyone being injured during the
OL,20,Fincident.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
