OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775386971
OL,3,CMan arrested following disorder after
OL,4,CMiddlesbrough match against Millwall
OL,6,FDetective Chief Superintendent Anne-
OL,7,FMarie Salwey said: "We are aware of
OL,8,Freports of disorder at and around
OL,9,FMiddlesbrough railway station
OL,10,Ffollowing the conclusion of today's
OL,11,Ffootball match.
OL,13,F"This involved several opposing
OL,14,Fsupporters fighting. At this stage, we
OL,15,Fare not aware of any member of the
OL,16,Fpublic having sustained any injuries.
OL,18,F"One man has been arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of violent disorder and has
OL,20,Fbeen taken into police custody.
OL,26,@oD@TOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
