FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775386971
OL,3,CMan arrested following disorder after
OL,4,CMiddlesbrough match against Millwall
OL,6,F"A number of officers had been
OL,7,Fdeployed to this fixture, including
OL,8,Fevidence gathering officer, and a full
OL,9,Fpostmatch investigation will now take
OL,10,Fplace to establish the circumstances
OL,11,Fand to identify and bring those
OL,12,Fresponsible to justice.
OL,14,F"This type of criminal behaviour has
OL,15,Fno place in football or our
OL,16,Fcommunities."
OL,26,@vD@AOU
