OL,6,FThe police are encouraging anyone who
OL,7,Fwas in the area at the time or who
OL,8,Fwitnessed the disorder to contact them
OL,9,Fon 101 or visiting the Cleveland
OL,10,Fpolice website quoting reference
OL,11,Fnumber 056241.
